Lol! You&#39;re not the only that&#39;s been questioning their sanity at times here lately... Some of the stuff I hear is just plain perplexing, and then it gets even more so when others say they don&#39;t hear it.

I&#39;ve only discovered ghost box two months ago, and at first my husband and I took it to cemeteries, but the most interesting things I&#39;ve captured have been at home, I believe.  I plan to keep using it at various locations, but also at home.  At home I keep getting the strangest communications that sound as if there are people in various scenarios talking to each other, oblivious to my presence (places like shopping at a market, an auction, an ambulance scene, pilots in airplane - this is what I&#39;m inferring from what I&#39;m hearing).  So far I&#39;ve not been able to get validation from others of what I&#39;m hearing, but I keep thinking that something is there, and not just broadcast fragments.  Only time will tell if this is the case or not.  So far, it is still possible that I am wrong due to the fact that I have not amassed that many examples of it yet, and the simple fact that I&#39;m new to GBC and my ears are not trained... however, I would also be wrong to deny to myself what my ears are hearing... I spent enough of my life doing that, denying what I sense, just to fit in with others/society.  I&#39;m no longer into doing that, otherwise I wouldn&#39;t even be found on a forum like this :)

